HAPPY NEW YEAR!!!!

Let’s kick the year off right—with A NEW STORY!

Follow the link below to start reading Wildcard, a small town sports romcom I’ve been working on for a long, long while and that I love desperately. I’m so excited to finally share it with you! 

So far readers are saying things like:
“That was probably the hottest and nastiest thing I’ve ever read from you and I am 100% here for it!” - @ali_chesh_ca

Here’s how it works:
1. Follow the link to go to Kindle Vella 
2. The first three episodes are free, then you’ll pay tokens for the following chapters, usually about 13-25c per chapter (by wordcount!)
3. Ten episodes are available now with new episodes coming out on Mon, Wed, Fri, Sun. 
4. Hit the follow button to get an alert when a new episode drops!
5. You can read on your phone, Kindle, or iPad! Just navigate to your Kindle app and then to SHORTS in the bottom menu!
6. If you hate this format, NEVER FEAR! The final version of the book will be released in April <3 

WILDCARD
Remy Winfield’s house is the last place I expect to stay for my best friend’s wedding in her home town of Roseville, Tennessee. Without options, I have no choice but to move into his cottage’s spare room, the beastly baseball player with more muscles than manners. He’s on a mission to get me into bed by way of the filthiest mouth I’ve ever known. I might be a Lady, but I can still play his dirty little game, so long as it stays between us. And I’ll be damned if I crack first.

LINK IN BIO! ❤️❤️❤️ happy reading, i missed you 🥹🫶🏻
